    <p>Last year 1dece.ro wanted to <a href="/2012/index.html" class="link">“move the capital of Romania”</a> and this year's goal is to create the first and largest digital <i>hora</i>.</p>
    <p><strong>HORA</strong> you say?</p>
    <p>Yes, <i>hora</i> is a traditional Romanian folk dance where the dancers hold each other's hands forming a circle. The dance is usually accompanied by musical instruments.</p>
